summary:
An enthusiastic law graduate with a strong willingness to explore different business types and learn new things.

In recent years, I've gained some valuable experience working at a law firm based in Slovenia, dealing with multilingual Hungarian-Slovenian clients. After that, while working as an assistant with a company arranging online payment solutions, I became familiar with the payment industry. 

My evergrowing interest in modern financial technologies has lead me to move to Amsterdam and start working at a European based Payment Institution.
